			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Recon (in order):\r\n1. oe readyattackonden\r\n2. oe attackondenraidervictory\r\n3. SetGlobalOsirisFlag DEN_AttackOnDen_Event_GoblinPartyInvitation\r\n4. Roll amazing\r\n5. Go to camp\r\n6. Talk to Minthara. A mindmeld seduction scene will happen. Agree to spend the night with her.\r\n7. Go to bed\r\n8. Choose to spend the night with Minthara, and sex scene will happen.\r\n9.  Dialog will trigger after. "
				},
